Net-Stitcho

A module to use with the Stitcho.com notification service.

Only useful for partner users of the service.

Allows you to use the APIs from your Perl code.



INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Net::Stitcho

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Net-Stitcho

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Net-Stitcho

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Net-Stitcho

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Net-Stitcho


